results.title: Out
results.description: Sammy sings to the feds and they put together a profile of Matt Murdock as Daredevil; The boss tells his men to keep the info under wraps, but the next morning, Foggy buys the Daily Globe which has a headline story about his best friend being DD.

results.title: [The Secret Is Out]
results.description: Foggy and Matt desperately try to figure out what to do now that Matt's secret ID is known to the world.

results.title: Jay Leno and Spider-Man: One Night Only Part 3
[I Didn't Know You Knew]
results.description: Ben and Parker tell Jonah the DD secret identity story is a hoax but both refuse to tell him who Daredevil really is; Foggy tries to get Matt to give up his life as Daredevil.

results.title: [I'm Not Afraid of You]
results.description: After helping Spidey mop up Mr. Hyde, Matt calls a press conference to clear up the allegations that he is, in fact, Daredevil; The conference begins as the issue ends.

results.title: [One Hundred Percent Untrue]
results.description: Matt denies to the press that he and Daredevil are one and the same; The Widow tries to coax Matt into going out with her as DD but is turned down flat; Matt meets with Vanessa who informs him that she is leaving the country for good and has sold the Kingpin's business to an unnamed buyer; Elektra shows up for a last panel confrontation with Matt.

results.title: [Dancing Between the Raindrops]
results.description: Matt has a little rooftop chat with Elektra; The Daily Globe lawyer bluntly assures Matt and Foggy that the secret identity trial is going to court; DD spooks the FBI Agent who is going to testify and Mr. Rosenthal calls Matt in to settle; After a settlement is reached, Rosenthal decides to take the battle to court anyway since Matt is so smug about it all.

results.title: [The Trial of the Century Part 1]
results.description: Power Man and Iron Fist try to get Matt to help the White Tiger beat an unfair murder rap.

results.title: The Trial of the Century Part 2
results.description: Matt and Foggy defend Hector against the murder charge brought against him.

items.name: Daredevil Visionaries: Kevin Smith (Daredevil Vol. I: Guardian Devil) (1999)
Daredevil Visionaries: Kevin Smith (Daredevil Vol. I: Guardian Devil) (Trade Paperback)

results.title: Guardian Devil Part 4: The Devil's Distaff
results.description: Matt spends some time with his mother to get his head together; Macabes hires Bullseye to bring back the child.

items.name: Daredevil Visionaries: Kevin Smith (Daredevil Vol. I: Guardian Devil) (1999)
Daredevil Visionaries: Kevin Smith (Daredevil Vol. I: Guardian Devil) (Trade Paperback)

results.title: [The Trial of the Century Part 3]
results.description: When his trial ends with a guilty verdict, Hector takes matters into his own hands.

results.title: Lowlife Part 1
results.description: DD saves a blind girl from being hit by a truck; Wilbur Day turns in his stilts to Murdock and tells him that the Owl has taken over the Kingpin's turf; DD begins his quest to bring the Owl down.

results.title: Lowlife Part 2
results.description: DD continues to interfere with the Owl's underworld business; Milla visits Murdock to see if he is Daredevil; Rosenthal is killed while taking a swim.

results.title: Lowlife Part 3
results.description: Mr. Rosenthal's body is found; Milla and Matt decide to go on a date, but Foggy tries to talk his friend out of it; Matt asks Cage to help him with the Owl situation and gets a good reprimand, "Sweet Christmas" style.

results.title: Lowlife Part 4
results.description: Matt and Milla's date is interrupted by the police who want to question Matt about the death of Mr. Rosenthal.

results.title: Lowlife Part 5
results.description: Matt tries to apologize to Milla for their interrupted date, takes down the Owl as DD and learns that the Kingpin is back in town.

results.title: Hardcore Part 1
results.description: Kingpin pulls Mary out of her "normal" life as a soap opera star and back on the road to insanity; Milla decides to try and get closer to Matt; Fisk begins to consolidate his power and return to his role as the Kingpin of Crime; Matt and Milla start out on a date which is interrupted by Typhoid Mary setting Matt on fire.

results.title: Hardcore Part 2
results.description: Story focuses on Fisk's bid for power in trying to return as the Kingpin of crime; Story ends at the same time and in the same way as issue #46, with Typhoid Mary interrupting Matt and Milla's date by setting Matt on fire.

results.title: Hardcore Part 3
results.description: Matt protects Milla from Typhoid with the help of Luke and Jessica; Bullseye shows up at Fisk's looking for his old job back.

results.title: Hardcore Part 4
results.description: Bullseye shows up at Matt's place to kill another one of his girlfriends; DD takes Bullseye down hard and carves the crosshair tattoo into his forehead with a knife.

items.name: Daredevil Visionaries: Kevin Smith (Daredevil Vol. I: Guardian Devil) (1999)
Daredevil Visionaries: Kevin Smith (Daredevil Vol. I: Guardian Devil) (Trade Paperback)

results.title: Guardian Devil Part 5: Devil's Despair
results.description: Strange lets DD know that he has been duped in much that has gone on and he summons Mephisto to prove it; DD races to the church to save the child, his mother and Karen from the deadly Bullseye but isn't quite successful.

items.name: Daredevil Visionaries: Kevin Smith (Daredevil Vol. I: Guardian Devil) (1999)
Daredevil Visionaries: Kevin Smith (Daredevil Vol. I: Guardian Devil) (Trade Paperback)

results.title: Hardcore Part 5
results.description: Tired of the invasions into his life and years of dealing with the evils of Wilson Fisk, DD beats the Kingpin to a pulp and declares himself the new Kingpin of New York City.

items.name: Daredevil Vol. 8: Echo – Vision Quest (Trade Paperback)

results.title: Echo Part One
results.description: Echo begins her origin story and explains her relationship with Daredevil and the Kingpin.

items.name: Daredevil Vol. 8: Echo – Vision Quest (Trade Paperback)
Daredevil Vol. 8: Echo – Vision Quest (Trade Paperback)
Daredevil Vol. 8: Echo – Vision Quest (Trade Paperback)

results.title: Echo Part 2
results.description: Maya confronts Matt about their past relationship, continues her origin story and ends up talking to the man who helped raise her, the Kingpin.
